commits.sourceNew: /** * Copy a file from specified sourceRepo to the destination directory (i.e. restore). * * @param sourceRepo * The source URI hosting the file to be copied. * @param fileName * The name of the file to by copied * @param dest * The destination where the file should be copied. * @throws IOException * in case of errors. */ void copyFileTo(URI sourceRepo, String fileName, Directory dest) throws IOException;
